floatproperty.notes: Value is in centimeters per second squared. Negative is down. Default is Earth gravity. Do not set to a value >= 0.
Multiplier value for gravity on rigid body. A rigid body is defined as a body on which the distance between two points never changes whatever be the force applied on it.
Max Z difference between two planes that a pawn can transition up onto. Settings this to a high value can lead to some ridiculous (and buggy feeling) results
